  <source>University Hospital, Linkoeping</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To study the effect of mild laser treatment on the incidence of exudative complications in
      soft drusen maculopathy. We hypothesise that mild laser treatment causing a proliferation of
      the retinal pigment epithelium and enhancing the capacity of clearing drusen material from
      Bruch's membrane.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
